<br />
<br />- You focus on one that seems popular and that you like or
<br />- You go generic and cover the most popular one with a plug-in approach
<br />
<br />The first one is the easiest to do. The second may give you a hard time but would cover more users along the way. It all depends on how much time and effort you can put on it.  My hobby time became almost non existent recently so I had to put that project on indefinite hold.

		

